<title>FAITH IS THE VICTORY!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Vakna tangzawl chungah kikulh,
 Kristien sepaih, tho un;
 Kidona chu bawl zawm zel un,
 Zan thim ahung tun ma'n;
 Nuoi zinmang galdo a pangin,
 I theihtawp suoh hitiu,
 Ginna zawhna a hih I heu,
 Khawvel pum nuoisieh chu!

[V2]
 Ginna zawhna ahi (2)
 Aw, zawhna lopi tak chuh,
 Khawvel pum nuoisieh chuh.

[V3]
 2. A puonlap Hehpihna ahi,
 I chemzam uh A thu;
 Mithiengte hawhsa lampi ah,
 Guolzo zelin I chieh;
 Ginna'n chinpei banga hatin,
 Muntin a na zo ui;
 Thihna a zawhnau Ginna chuh,
 I awmphawu chuh ahi.

[V4]
 3. Muntin ah dogal a um ui,
 Lauhum a kithuom in;
 Mawkum loin masuon hitiu,
 Kidona mun zuonin;
 Hukdamna lukhuk khu chietin,
 Thutak a kawng gakin,
 I chiehna chengah gal zam ding,
 Zawhna aw'n gamthawng ding.

[V5]
 4. Kuole gal zote kawm a chun,
 Zawhna puon vam piena;
 Angelte masang ah vanah,
 Amin chuh phuon hina;
 Vakna tangzawl akipat in,
 Hehpihna lunggil in;
 Zan dogal chuh tai vek un au,
 Isu zawhna minin.</lyrics>
</song>